          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-dark mb-4 font-heading">VitalEdge Wellness Platform</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-dark mb-6">
            Advanced wellness technology that empowers employees to take control of their health while helping employers reduce healthcare costs.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-neutral-dark">Biometric screenings and health assessments</span>
